text:
Or Login / Register With Us Forgot Password? Remember Me Dal Shabet's Subin is stunning in red for 'Circle's Dream' jacket photos By jennywill 27 minutes ago 1,722 300 3 0 Google+ Dal Shabet 's Subin has released jacket photos for her upcoming " Circle's Dream "!
The upcoming single will be finishing up her solo project by tying "Circle's Dream" and " Strawberry " onto her previous songs " Moon " and " Swing ". She portrayed innocence in the first two songs, and in these two songs she'll be portraying first experiences as well as the pain that comes with them. 
Her songs will be out on February 23 at midnight KST. YOU MAY LIKE GET AKP IN YOUR INBOX! ..or follow allkpop to stay updated: Tags:
